import React, {useEffect} from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import {element} from "prop-types"; const TotalBudget = () => { let budgetDetail = [] useEffect(() => { budgetDetail = [] axios.get(`http://localhost:8080/assets/test`) .then((response) => { console.log(`TotalBudget useEffect then`) response.data.map(element => { budgetDetail.push(element) }) }) .catch((error) => { console.log(`TotalBudget useEffect catch`) throw error }) }, [budgetDetail]) return <>
내 자산 총액
{budgetDetail} 원 		평가 수익률 {budgetDetail} %
평가 손익 {budgetDetail} 원
} export default TotalBudget;
